summary: TL* THE CONTACT OWNS A 2019 TOYOTA CAMRY. THE CONTACT DISCOVERED WHILE ATTEMPTING TO SELL HIS VEHICLE, THAT THE VEHICLE WAS INCLUDED IN NHTSA CAMPAIGN NUMBER: 20V682000 (FUEL SYSTEM, GASOLINE) HOWEVER, THE PART TO DO THE RECALL REPAIR WAS UNAVAILABLE. TOYOTA 101 (386 CONVENTION WAY, REDWOOD CITY, CA 94063) WAS CONTACTED AND IT WAS CONFIRMED THAT PARTS WERE NOT YET AVAILABLE. THE MANUFACTURER WAS MADE AWARE OF THE ISSUE AND OFFERED NO ASSISTANCE. THE CONTACT HAD NOT EXPERIENCED A FAILURE. PARTS DISTRIBUTION DISCONNECT.
